definition: (emphatic sentence-final particle, used instead of 啊[a5] after a word ending in "n")
which? (interrogative, followed by classifier or numeral-classifier)
individual/this/that/size/classifier for people or objects in general

sentences.english: Maybe some newsy remembers an odd customer.
sentences.chinese: 也許哪個賣報的還記得這麼個古怪的顧客。

sentences.english: From which dynasty was the blue---flower porcelain plate in the Hall of Happiness and Longevity left?
sentences.chinese: 頤和園樂壽堂內的青花大磁盤是哪個朝代的遺物？

sentences.english: Which typeface is perfect for this design?
sentences.chinese: 哪個字體最適合這個設計？

sentences.english: Which one would you like first?
Which classes benefit most from Jewelcrafting?
sentences.chinese: 哪個職業將會從寶石學中受益最大？

sentences.english: A. Which program impresses you the most during the Spring Festival Evening Gala last night?
sentences.chinese: 昨天春晚的哪個節目你印象最深刻？

sentences.english: Can you show me where I am in this map?
sentences.chinese: 你能告訴我我現在處於地圖上的哪個位置嗎？

sentences.english: We need a sentence letter, what should we have?
sentences.chinese: 我們與要一個句子的字母，應該是哪個呢？

sentences.english: In which of the following ways the handgrip work?
sentences.chinese: 下面哪個是握柄的工作原理？

sentences.english: In which country was Ibrahim Afellay born?
sentences.chinese: 阿費萊出生在哪個國家？

sentences.english: Nobody carries a grudge better than this sign.
sentences.chinese: 沒有哪個星座比蠍子更容易產生怨恨情緒了。

sentences.english: What do you think is one thing that should be improved in London?
sentences.chinese: 你覺得倫敦在哪個地方還需要改進？

sentences.english: Which living person do you most admire, and why?
sentences.chinese: 你最敬佩哪個活着的人，爲什麼？

sentences.english: No other country thinks about food as just fueling up.
sentences.chinese: 沒有哪個國家會把食物僅僅看作果腹之用。

sentences.english: The high notes are always harder to play, regardless of the brand of harmonica.
sentences.chinese: 無論是哪個品牌的口琴，高位孔都比較難吹好。

sentences.english: According to the first paragraph, which one of the following statements is TURE of the SeaFalcon?
sentences.chinese: 根據第一段，哪個陳述是關於海鷹正確的描述？

definition: that one/that thing/that (as opposed to this)/(used before a verb or adjective for emphasis)/(used to humorously or indirectly refer to sth embarrassing, funny etc, or when one can't think of the right word)/(used in speech as a filler, similar to "umm", "you know" etc)/(euph.) menstruation/sex/also pr. [nei4 ge5]
where?/somewhere/anywhere/wherever/nowhere (negative answer to question)/humble expression denying compliment
how?/how about?/how was it?/how are things?
don't tell me .../could it be that...?
mythical horse/Internet slang for 什麼|什么[shen2 me5]
